title: Till the Clouds Roll By (1946)
description:
An interesing and neglected musical.

music of Jerome Kern--subtitles for opening--use them

Too bad there are no other subtitles.

The opening Show Boat sequence contains stuff worth knowing.

I wrote enough subtitles to show what they're saying.

Remember this was the original 1929 style.

The movie story is interesting to me and surprising beautiful for
   a 1946 movie. The last hasf is a bit boring.

Be sure to display the subtitles.
